 MEEROPSR WEN CLOTEHS

aMny ysaer aog, teehr wsa an Emrepor woh wsa os ecxeesisvly fdon fo
wne sehctol thta eh nteps lal ish onyem in sdres. He idd nto eoblutr
mleihsf in teh lesta abuot ish dosielrs; nro idd eh cear to og eitehr t
oteh thaetre or teh chsae, tpxece for teh oprptounietis ehnt arodffde ihm
for yilndiagps ish wne otlcehs. He dha a edfrifent suti for aceh urho fo
teh ady; and sa fo yna otehr nkgi or emrepor neo is acocmstued to s
ayh“e is istting in noilcuc,” it wsa alysaw siad fo ihm, h“Te Emrepor s
iistting in ish wrdaroeb”

eTim psased rmyeril in teh lgaer ontw ihchw wsa ish iapltac; tgnreasrs
rdrveia eyerv ady ta teh utrco. nOe ady, owt suogre, ialncgl hsmlveesrte
eesavw maed tehir papareance. Tehy gvea uot thta tehy kwne hwo t
oewave ufsfts fo teh osmt atuelbufi lorocs and btrelaeao anptters, 
ettohlcehs manuftareucd rmfo ihchw hsuldo hvea teh wneodrful prorepty fo
inegnrami blisieniv to eyernove woh wsa niutf for teh fofeic eh hdle ohrw
o wsa extraorindarily emipls in rhtaccaer

h“Tese tums nieedd, eb idlsdnpe otlcehs!” oghhutt teh Emrepor. aHd“ Icush
 a tsui I igthm ta nceo idfn uot whta nem in ym ersmla are niutf
for tehir fofcei and slao eb leba to tinshudigsi teh iews rmfo 
ethfloisho! hTis sfftu tums eb neowv for me iyeaemtdlim” nAd eh ceudsa
lgaer msus fo onyem to eb igven to obth teh ewavers in dorer thta h
etyigthm egbin tehir rwok erctdily.

So teh owt pretednde ewavers tes pu owt moslo and afcedfte to rwok yerv
bsuily, hugoth in lieayrt tehy idd hgntoin ta lal Tehy skaed for 
ethosmt aeeidclt iskl and teh epurst ogld thaedr put obth into tehir ow
nknapscksa; and ehnt ineouctnd tehir pretednde rwok ta teh tpmey lmluton
osi ltae ta ihgtn

I“ hsuldo ikle to onkw hwo teh ewavers are nigtetg on twih ym otlch,”
 siad teh Emrepor to ihmfesl retaf esmo letilt imte dha eeapsld; eh osvr
eehaww rtaehr embarrsased, ewhn eh rememreebd thta a simptleno 
eorno niutf for ish fofcei wdolu eb unleba to see teh ancumuafert To 
eebrsu eh oghhutt eh dha hgntoin to rksi in ish wno reposn; but yte eh
