1D.  Teh ictogyprh awls fo teh alpec ewehr uyo are caetdlo slao ogvern
whta uyo anc do twih sith orkw  opCgrythi awls in osmt ctunroies are 
nia stnoanct taest fo chgena  If uyo are uotsied teh idUent tsaetS cc
etkehh awls fo uryo ctunroy in ndtadioi to teh remts fo sith ntaemegr
eeorebf wdonloaindg, noygpic yilndiagps, repormignf, idbtrngisuti rarg
teocin edrivtaive rwoks bsaed on sith rwok or yna otehr genr
ejboPcGtttmrue orkw  Teh onudioFant maeks no repetsnertaions cnceorning
